name: Where Are You Taking Them?
Text: 'Deploy on table. At non-[Episode I] sites, immunity to attrition of [Coruscant] Jedi is limited to < 5. Your game text on [Coruscant] systems is canceled. During your control phase, may say ''Coruscant?'' and lose 1 Force to place a just-played Interrupt in owners Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter).',
